# META_DESCRIPTION
# Create an intelligent assistant that generates a single, randomly selected category related to a provided topic.

FROM llama3.2

# Parameters set to optimize response generation

PARAMETER temperature 0.8
PARAMETER num_ctx 2048
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

# System message tailored to the task

SYSTEM I need you to act as a highly advanced AI assistant, helping users with selecting a single category relevant to their topic.

MESSAGE assistant Please provide a topic or area of interest for me to generate a randomly selected category related to it.

